Package com.teamviewer.sdk.screensharing

package com.teamviewer.sdk.screensharing
Contains interfaces and classes for interacting with the TeamViewer Screen Sharing Sdk.
  • Class
    Description
    AccessControlCallback
    Callback for authentication of access control requests from the remote supporter.
    AccessControlData
    This interface provides the callback and more information about the AccessControl.

    Callback to provide the result of the AccessControl.

    Rules for access control.
